{"title":"在RaspberryPi上安装LAMP","url":"/raspberrypi-install-lamp/","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>浙江大学嵌入式系统课程</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>既然已经在RaspberryPi上安装了Linux系统，很自然的我们可以想到在其上安装LAMP，使其变为随身服务器。</p>\n<p>本文设备环境：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Raspberry Pi B板</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>系统镜像：2012-12-16-wheezy-raspbian.img[<a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/share/link?shareid=318970&amp;uk=3842409107\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">下载</a>]</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>图文攻略：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>使用putty连接并登陆Raspberry</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301214608.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301214644.png\" alt=\"\"><br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>更新软件源</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> apt-get update</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301215805.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>安装LAMP</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> apt-get install apache2 php5 mysql-server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301220037.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>安装完成，开始配置LAMP</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置MySQL的root账户的密码；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301220725.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>重复一遍刚刚设置的root的密码；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301220736.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>其余的按默认配置自动设置；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301221327.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>为了方便管理MySQL，接下来安装phpMyAdmin；</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> apt-get install phpmyadmin</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301221522.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>选择apache2，高亮后按空格选中，回车；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301221641.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用默认配置即可，选择Yes；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301221936.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>输入之前设置的MySQL的root账户密码；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301221955.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置用于phpMyAdmin在数据库中注册所用的密码，之后有重复输入验证；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301222013.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>设置/var/www/目录的所有者和权限；</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /var/</div><div class=\"line\">id pi</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> chown -R pi:pi www/</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> chmod -R <span class=\"number\">755</span> www/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301223345.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>在/var/www/目录中新建一个index.php文件；</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">vi index.php</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>文件内容如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">&lt;?php</span></div><div class=\"line\"> phpinfo();</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">?&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在浏览器中打开 <a href=\"http://IP/index.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">http://IP/index.php</a> （IP即你的Raspberry的IP），可看到如下图所示的页面。至此，RaspberryPi上LAMP的搭建就基本结束了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301224143.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>打开地址 <a href=\"http://IP/phpmyadmin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">http://IP/phpmyadmin/</a> 可以打开phpMyAdmin，如下图所示；</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301222509.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>用MySQL的root账户登录，即可很方便的对MySQL进行管理了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301222539.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>附加内容</strong></p>\n<p>要管理RaspberryPi上的服务器，可以使用filezilla等软件通过SSH登录，类似于FTP管理。</p>\n<p>这里以WinSCP为例。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>打开WinSCP，点击右上角的新建按钮，填入服务器信息；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301234118.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>输入完毕后点击保存，（可以选择保存密码），选择刚刚新建的会话，点击登录；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301222639.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>在文件浏览器中定位到/var/www/目录，上传网页文件即可。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301222723.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>如下图，是我用Raspberry Pi运行之前做的数据库大程的截图。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.nilennoct.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Unnamed-QQ-Screenshot20130301224540.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>至此本文就结束啦，Enjoy it!</p>\n<p>若文中存在错误，欢迎斧正^_^</p>\n","layout":"post"}